{"tid":1373810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣反攻大陸既入黎傾下","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:56:32.000Z","uid":271284,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f94008526077b3a5e14c63f5ddb9e23e055314b9","tid":1373810,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"最近同個國內既藍絲朋友傾左好耐，成功將佢變黃。佢話我知，大陸入面淨係知香港亂，根本唔知我地爭取緊乜，而最重要係，我地d文宣方向全部錯曬，就算見到都無人會睇<br />\n<br />\n大陸人根本唔在乎咩民主，唔好同佢地講咩民主理念，咩黑警，咩黑社會，佢地會全部WFC<br />\n<br />\n佢地關心既只有錢！你要同佢講：中聯辦搞亂香港騙國家維穩費，每年騙幾百億！中聯辦在香港買左300幾個單位，總共40億，全部係呃中國人民既血汗錢既！佢地一定信，然後你再同佢講，香港人好慘，比中聯辦利用黎呃國家錢，佢地就會明白啦<br />\n<br />\n如果可以搵到中聯辦官員生活奢華，有幾多個架車，幾多個情婦咁<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係，同中國人講野係唔使講證據既，最緊要你個故事啱聽，中聯辦就水洗都唔清架啦！"},{"pid":"80e167d49e8d9386a5282cf72b12c3a9c42ac5b1","tid":1373810,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db9eb17d23e4e4a8126a71eda44db1e0ca53f7a","tid":1373810,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfd937a6a94e6ea53a1d94509870ef8cbe14d9f","tid":1373810,"uid":281895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3rPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=df79b9d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面 china folder  有一部份關於中國的資訊"},{"pid":"66fe04efd0b3ff7e2ae3ca2af407591d2782c785","tid":1373810,"uid":281895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cfd937a6a94e6ea5